      • setTimeout

        public static void setTimeout(int timeoutFast,
                              int timeoutMiddle,
                              int timeoutSlow)
        set timeout, enable set different timeout with different network type.
        when set different timeout with single timeout meanwhile, the latest config will function.
        every net request will check current network type to set suitable timeout value.
        参数:
        timeoutFast - Wifi、HSUPA、HSPA、LTE high network timeout
        timeoutMiddle - UMTS、EVDO revison A、EVDO revison B、HSDPA middle network timeout
        timeoutSlow - GPRS、EDGE、CDMA、EVDO revison 0、1xRTT、iDen、eHRPO low network timeout
